description: Ron came by to explain to Shayne why he would not be able to pay him the money he owes him. Shayne was not willing to hear any excuses but did give Ron a chance to pay off the debt another way. Ron had to give up his ass and Shayne took the whole payment. Ron never thought his whole face would be covered with a load from Shayne but Shayne sure did prove him wrong.
title: Man Juice
